{"published time": "2024-03-18T16:21:00+08:00", "images": ["https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/cd149150-ec80-4e48-bd49-f2d182b59afb-e1710771580319.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/5e67536c-4f31-4242-82ee-5d5856ccd89c.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/643e34f1-cbff-45e2-908b-da32924d1b24.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/b1fbcef6-ea30-4ac7-af52-4fd4a3fb5296.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/dd056255-5b59-40b4-8065-86675516c00d.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/3dbee8e4-b6d4-4f40-8c2c-bf36cdd848e4.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo_5458370037388793318_y.jpg"], "content": "<div class=\"single-content\"><figure class=\"post-thumbnail\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" height=\"582\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-18T16-21-00-08-00/000000.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-18T16-21-00-08-00/000000.jpg\" width=\"800\"/></figure><!-- .post-thumbnail --><p><strong>The unified electronic register of conscripts, servicemen and reservists \"Oberig\" is a tool for military accounting of citizens. It aims to reduce the number of errors as a result of the human factor and save resources of the state and human being through digitalization.</strong></p><p>About this<a href=\"https://t.me/ministry_of_defense_ua/9105\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">informs</a>Ministry of Defence Ukraine.</p><p>One of the advantages of the Oberig Register is to prevent corruption.</p><p>\"Thanks to the registry, every step of data change is tracked and confirmed by an electronic signature,\" the defense department said.</p><p>Currently, the Ministry of Defense, together with partners, is working to create an electronic military accounting document.</p><p>\"This is an excerpt from a registry, which will testify to the accounting status of a citizen - where he is registered, or is suitable for service, etc.\", - said at MOU.</p><div class=\"fotorama--wp\" data-auto=\"false\" data-captiontag=\"dd\" data-columns=\"0\" data-icontag=\"dt\" data-ids=\"552702,552701,552700,552699,552698,552704\" data-itemtag=\"dl\" data-link=\"file\" data-max-width=\"100%\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-size=\"large\" data-width=\"1280\"><div class=\"gallery galleryid-552693 gallery-columns-0 gallery-size-thumbnail\" id=\"gallery-1\"><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-18T16-21-00-08-00/000001.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-18T16-21-00-08-00/000001.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-18T16-21-00-08-00/000002.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-18T16-21-00-08-00/000002.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-18T16-21-00-08-00/000003.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-18T16-21-00-08-00/000003.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-18T16-21-00-08-00/000004.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-18T16-21-00-08-00/000004.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-18T16-21-00-08-00/000005.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-18T16-21-00-08-00/000005.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-18T16-21-00-08-00/000006.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-18T16-21-00-08-00/000006.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl></div></div><div style=\"margin: 20px 0; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 8px 20px 10px; background: #f1f1f1; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.15); box-shadow: 0 5px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.3); font-size:15px; border-radius: 8px;\">The only electronic register \"Oberig\" was modernized with the support of the European Union within the Eu4digitalua project, which is implemented by the Estonian Academy of Electronic Management.</div><p>As reported<a href=\"https://armyinform.com.ua/2024/03/01/oberig-vzhe-pidklyuchyvsya-do-najbilshyh-reyestriv/\">Armyinform</a>, the register of conscripts \"Oberig\" has already been connected to the largest registers.</p><p>Before<a href=\"https://armyinform.com.ua/2024/02/27/u-minoborony-gotuyut-sertyfikat-zahysnyka-yakyj-mozhna-bude-otrymaty-z-reyestru-oberig/\">It became known</a>that in the Oberig Register it will be possible to obtain a certificate of defender.</p></div>", "source": "https://armyinform.com.ua/2024/03/18/reyestr-vijskovozobovyazanyh-oberig-yak-praczyuye-i-dlya-chogo-potriben/", "title": "Register of conscripts \"Oberig\": how works and what is needed for", "description": "The Ministry of Defense of Ukraine informs about it. One of the advantages of the Oberig Register \u2014...", "author": ["Army Inform"], "categories": ["\u041d\u043e\u0432\u0438\u043d\u0438"], "tags": ["\u0440\u0435\u0454\u0441\u0442\u0440 \u00ab\u041e\u0431\u0435\u0440\u0456\u0433\u00bb"], "source_name": "ArmyInform"}